it features not\nsignificantly different from that due to the normal gas regime. The\nheterogeneity across FL, found to be present both in bulk and confined systems,\nmight cause the breakdown of the universal scaling between structure and\ndynamics of fluids necessitating the determination of a unique relationship\nbetween them.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Jan 2018 19:29:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-29"}
