ies, we show\nthat at late times the kinetic energy presents a characteristic slope of\n$\\epsilon^{-2}$ in the high-energy region.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Jan 2018 02:33:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 29 Apr 2018 18:40:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-27"}
